    purpose: "This policy ensures the service meets its legal duty to display its most recent performance rating conspicuously — at premises and online — and uses ratings and inspection findings honestly in all communications. Display is a transparency duty owed to the people who use and choose the service; getting it wrong is both an enforceable breach and a fast way to look evasive.",
